eu.europa.esig.dss.x509.ocsp

Interface OCSPSource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    RevocationSource<OCSPToken>, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CAdESOCSPSource, ExternalResourcesOCSPSource, ListOCSPSource, OfflineOCSPSource, OnlineOCSPSource, PAdESOCSPSource, XAdESOCSPSource

    public interface OCSPSource
extends RevocationSource<OCSPToken>
    Typed sub-interface which allows to collect OCSPToken. The validation of a certificate may require the use of OCSP information. Theses information can be provided by multiple sources (the signature itself, online OCSP server, ...). This interface provides an abstraction for a source of OCSPResp
